R.I.P. Arleen Sorkin It's been a while since we checked in on Harley, Ivy, and the pure insanity that is the Harley Quinn Animated TV Show. We have a lot to catch up on as we do our best to tackle seasons 3 and 4, talk about the more significant themes of the series and marvel at how it manages to juggle raunchy humor with life lessons about love, identity and being human. This is the LAST STOP on the Major Issues Road To 300 episodes. Thank you to everyone who has supported us!

If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

